0211 - Beef Cattle Feedlots Summary > CUNNINGHAM CATTLE COMPANY PTY LTD is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover beef cattle feedlots. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. CUNNINGHAM CATTLE COMPANY PTY LTD is headquartered in Bondi Junction, New South Wales. It is headed by director & company secretary Bill Gunn. For the 2024 financial year, the company reported revenue of $34.54 million. Its net loss totalled $38.40 million. CUNNINGHAM CATTLE COMPANY PTY LTD forms part of the agriculture, forestry, and fishing industry sector.
